<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 800px; margin: 80px auto; padding: 0 20px; text-align: center; }
        h1 { font-size: 3rem; color: #e04444; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #555; }
        .requested-url { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 2px 6px; font-family: monospace; border-radius: 4px; color: #c0392b; }
        .home-btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; background: #0076ff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        .home-btn:hover { background: #0056b3; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
    <p>We couldn't find anything at <span class="requested-url"><%= url %></span></p>
    
    <a href="/" class="home-btn">Go Back Home</a>

</body>
</html>